text: haey chaur anak baoh nouv avei del mean now nung daisdam robsa anak choh noh vea nung leb trabeak nouv avei del puokke ban thveu . tampit avei del puokke ban thveu ku kreante chea kar baokabanhchhot robsa krou m nd akm bonnaoh . haey krou m nd akm min ach mean chychomneah laey tohbei chea ke mk pi ti nakadaoy
